title: Thomas Creek Archeological District
text: The Thomas Creek Archeological District is a <a href="United%20States">U.S.</a> <a href="Historic%20district%20%28United%20States%29">historic district</a> located east of <a href="Chumuckla%2C%20Florida">Chumuckla</a>, <a href="Florida">Florida</a>. On November 4, 1985, it was added to the U.S. <a href="National%20Register%20of%20Historic%20Places">National Register of Historic Places</a>.
